description: Scaling up Access to HIV Prevention, Treatment & Care supported by GFATM 7th round

subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened national capacities for implementation of HIV funds and programmes, including those financed through multilateral initiatives like the Global Fund to fight AIDS, Tuberculosis, and Malaria
subproject.description:
Pharmaceutical and test kits procured for :
1)	8,143 HIV patients
2)	253,000 sexually transmitted infection cases
3)	240,240 VCT test kits, and
4)	31,614 opportunistic infection (OI) cases
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: Scaling up Access to HIV Preve
